        "description": "**** 2.0 UPDATE: Passthrough and Hands! ****\nPlay Linelight in the real world with Passthrough, and control the game with your Hands! You can now enjoy Linelight in MR, and without controllers. It's pretty sweet!\n\nLinelight is a relaxing, wholesome puzzle game with a big heart. Picture getting a back massage while grooving to chill electronic beats, solving clever, award-winning puzzles, always ready to discover what surprises wait around the corner.\n\nPLAY LAYING DOWN\nFinally, a VR game you can play horizontally! You can optionally play laying down comfortably with the game above you. This is about as relaxing as technology gets.\n\nYA GONNA FEEL SMART\nYou are going to feel smart.\n\nYOU CAN DO EET\nThe only control is to move. So whether this is your first game or your thousandth, you can pick it up in just a few seconds.\n\nMUCH CONTENT\nThere are over 6 worlds chock-filled with ingenious puzzles and surprises, with a total of 6-8 hours of delightful content.\n\nQUOTES\n“Finding a game like Linelight feels like a blessing.” - GameSpot\n“Bursting with design smarts… For a chilled puzzling time, they don’t get much better than this.” - Rock Paper Shotgun\n“Pure, unadulterated gameplay.” - Polygon\n“Linelight is nothing short of a stroke of genius.” - Hardcore Gamer\n“A crowning achievement in the puzzle genre… An unforgettably unique gaming experience.” - OPNoobs (9/10)\n“Ingenious… The amount of times I said to myself ‘Ooh, that’s clever!’ was too numerous to count.” - God is a Geek (9/10)",
